issue.title: Can I use the approach named fetch directly?
issue.body:
When I look through recently updating, I can something I am confused, in the [ui/app/ducks/gas/gas.duck.js](https://github.com/AlwaysBCoding/emp-metamask/blob/b091470d27c20a9f052f353266236e519a10c7a9/ui/app/ducks/gas/gas.duck.js) at line 247:
```javascripts
fetch('https://ethgasstation.info/json/ethgasAPI.json', {
        'headers': {},
        'referrer': 'http://ethgasstation.info/json/',
        'referrerPolicy': 'no-referrer-when-downgrade',
        'body': null,
        'method': 'GET',
        'mode': 'cors'}
      )
```
I am not sure can I use `fetch` directly without any defining?
